tourBios.curYrHigh: Earned status with rounds of 73-72-68-72 at the Mackenzie Tour - PGA TOUR Canada Qualifying Tournament No. 1.
tourBios.carHigh: 2013: Made three starts on the Mackenzie Tour, making the cut in all three and playing his way into the season-ending Freedom 55 Financial Championship...Ended the season 90th on the Order of Merit as a non-member.
tourBios.personal: Enjoys tennis, skiing and baseball...Fan of Toronto Blue Jays and Toronto Maple Leafs...Was once roommates with fellow Mackenzie Tour member Riley Wheeldon in Orlando.
